text: Georgia Moir (born 5 December 1997) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * college- hosts-the-biggest-girls-water-polo-tournament * 18th-fina-world-championships * how-gwangju-fans Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
